{"word":"G89 - ἀδιαλείπτως - adialeíptōs - ad-ee-al-ipe'-toce - Without ceasing","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀδιαλείπτως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">adialeíptōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ad-ee-al-ipe'-toce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without ceasing</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இடைவிடாமல் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"without intermission, incessantly, assiduously"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G88 - ἀδιάλειπτος - adiáleiptos - ad-ee-al'-ipe-tos/88\">G88</a>; <i>uninterruptedly</i>, that is, <i>without omission</i> (on an appropriate occasion): - without ceasing.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}